('0248c987-e925-4fc8-aae6-a7a8c8f5fbe1', 65, 217, 'https://afamilycdn.com/2017/sp-1499586751522.jpg', '▫️Short review: A refreshing new beginning, though not without its shortcomings. Marvel has dressed Spider-Man in a high-school spirit—youthful, energetic, and vibrant. Yet the script falls slightly short in exploring the depth of Peter Parker, as portrayed by Tom Holland, while the film itself lacks both surprising turns and a truly impactful climax. ▫️Rating • Plot: 7.5 • Twist: 6.8 • Message: 7.8 • Acting: 8.0 • Cine: 8.6 • Pacing: 8.8 \n• MU&H:7.8 •VFX: 8.4 • Music: 7.0▫️Overall: 7.8 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Spider-Man: Homecoming', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/0248c987-e925-4fc8-aae6-a7a8c8f5fbe1', 3.9, '2025-11-24 11:42:32', '2025-11-24 11:42:32'),
('04c3986c-8ebe-495c-aeaa-ee90b4f20b94', 3, 6, 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQR5e-mTlbsllWUcPjUNoqA8_XQOmadgW39CZbSvkygktOv76YCihKwx7s&s=10', 'Some people make a living out of these😭💔', 'Feliz Navidad', 'Amongus X Roblox', 'luker_feller/04c3986c-8ebe-495c-aeaa-ee90b4f20b94', 5.0, '2025-03-03 00:55:05', '2025-03-03 00:55:05'),
('0543654f-eba1-413a-a863-498b02fc0f32', 76, 217, 'https://cdn.marvel.com/content/2x/unknown-1.jpeg', '▫️Short review: By centering Thanos as a tragic yet terrifying figure, the film delivers both grandeur and emotional weight. With impeccable pacing, groundbreaking visual effects, and an audacious ending that stunned global audiences, it stands as one of Marvel’s most daring and impactful achievements. ▫️Rating • Plot: 10 • Twist: 10 • Acting: 9.5 \n• Message: 8.0 • Cine: 9.0 • Pacing: 10 • VFX: 8.0 \n• MU&H: 8.9 • Music: 9.6 ▫️Overall: 9.2 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Avengers: Infinity War', 'MCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/0543654f-eba1-413a-a863-498b02fc0f32', 4.6, '2025-12-11 22:50:11', '2025-12-11 22:50:11'),
('0790f5ae-b4af-4bf0-9352-63852e5c058d', 33, 217, 'https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/i/d96bb958-4e6c-4ce0-9447-fbe226fbbecf/df7om1j-156601cc-4bc4-487d-ba18-d95920f198bb.jpg', 'Good', 'Tè', 'Fh', 'Akyl_Lee/0790f5ae-b4af-4bf0-9352-63852e5c058d', 4.5, '2025-09-05 07:36:19', '2025-09-05 07:36:19'),
('09ce181b-3a28-4965-b934-63ac0ea39d13', 16, 71, 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/5c/Albert_Bierstadt_-_Among_the_Sierra_Nevada%2C_California_-_Google_Art_Project.jpg', 'Ini bukan sekadar lukisan, ini adalah mahakarya yang membuka pandangan pada kemegahan alam. Cahaya keemasannya membelai puncak gunung, danau yang tenang memantulkan langit, dan hamparan hijau yang tak berujung menghadirkan rasa takzim. Sungguh karya agung dari seorang Albert Bierstadt.🍃🍃', 'Among the Sierra Nevada Mountains, California', 'View of the Sierra Nevada', 'diegormdhn/09ce181b-3a28-4965-b934-63ac0ea39d13', 5.0, '2025-08-08 17:46:20', '2025-08-08 17:46:20'),
('09d22646-3815-4cc6-93e6-d44306005559', 34, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/pv-target-images/fdf4e6d9aaf30b73c4754791079fd804740ab33c2f25bc568440555783d0774f.jpg', '▫️Short review: “Orphan” delivers a gripping blend of psychological tension and horror, anchored by Isabelle Fuhrman’s unforgettable performance. The film’s infamous twist reshapes the entire narrative, turning a familiar setup into something truly unsettling.', 'Orphan (2009)', 'Thriller', 'Akyl_Lee/09d22646-3815-4cc6-93e6-d44306005559', 4.1, '2025-09-06 13:28:51', '2025-09-06 13:28:51'),
('0b4b9e99-4fef-4404-994f-25ae45c2b0a6', 76, 217, 'https://avatars.mds.yandex.net/get-kinopoisk-image/4483445/ef0bbcd1-22c9-477f-a33a-e3d385d5b046/1080x', '▫️Short review: Absolute cinema! Love the way Marvel introduced its new character. The message hit me hard. The movie itself is not about saving the world, it’s about saving oneself. The ending might catch you off guard!!! ▫️Rating • Plot: 7.0 • Twist: 7.0 • Message: 9.0 • Acting: 8.0 \n• Cinematography: 9.0 • Pacing: 7.0 • Visual effect: 8.5 • Make up and hairstyling: 8.0 • Music / OST: 7.0 ▫️Overall: 7.8 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Thunderbolts*', 'MCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/0b4b9e99-4fef-4404-994f-25ae45c2b0a6', 3.9, '2025-12-11 09:26:59', '2025-12-11 09:26:59'),
('0d25f6ad-7117-4fb8-b743-fe05c300e6a7', 56, 217, 'https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/i/d96bb958-4e6c-4ce0-9447-fbe226fbbecf/df7om1j-156601cc-4bc4-487d-ba18-d95920f198bb.jpg', '▫️Short review: Chloé Zhao brought a uniquely singular film, setting it apart entirely from all pre Marvel movies. Its frame unfolds like a work of art—both visually arresting and epic in scope. Its cosmic story with awe and unexpected twists, though the crowded chars leaves minor gaps in the script. Eternals would never be a failure and hardly deserving the hates. ▫️Rating • Plot: 8.5 \n• Twist 8.8 • Acting: 8.8 • Cine: 10 • Pacing: 10 • VFX: 10 • M&HS: 10 • Music: 9.0 ▫️Overall: 9.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Eternals (2021)', 'MCU | 🔝10 Movies', 'Akyl_Lee/0d25f6ad-7117-4fb8-b743-fe05c300e6a7', 4.5, '2025-09-05 07:38:19', '2025-09-05 07:38:19'),
('0d2b46e0-9fde-4f23-93fa-321b92a5bb0a', 56, 217, 'https://cdn.marvel.com/content/1x/thunderboltsposter.jpeg', '▫️Short review: Unique storytelling and unexpectedly emotional. The film redefines the superhero image by delving into inner pain, weaving subtle humor with authentic emotional drive, and creating a narrative that feels both real and deeply affecting.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 7.0 • Twist: 7.0 • Message: 9.0 \n• Acting: 8.0 • Cinematography: 9.0 • Pacing: 7.0 \n• VFX: 8.5 • Make up and hairstyling: 8.0 • Music: 7.0 ▫️Overall: 7.8 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Thunderbolts*', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/0d2b46e0-9fde-4f23-93fa-321b92a5bb0a', 3.9, '2025-09-05 07:30:07', '2025-09-05 07:30:07'),
('0f563c66-a2f2-4a0c-a348-80a2f2c6b5ef', 39, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDRjY2E0ZmEtN2QwNi00NTEwLWI3MWItODNkMGYwYWFjNGE0XkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_.jpg', '▫️Short review: A mid debut for the new Captain America, with engaging yet uneven storytelling. Lacking the sharp intensity like The Winter Soldier, and the central conflict feels unresolved. Still, waiting for the new Captain’s return in a future film that recaptures the action-driven spirit of earlier ones.\n ▫️Rating • Plot: 6.8 • Twist: 6.0 • Message: 6.5 • Acting: 7.5 • Cinematography: 7.0 • Pacing: 7.0 • Visual effect: 7.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 7.0 \n• Music / OST: 7.5 ▫️Overall:', 'Captain America: Brave New World', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/0f563c66-a2f2-4a0c-a348-80a2f2c6b5ef', 3.4, '2025-08-23 06:33:54', '2025-08-23 06:33:54'),
('10207441-2d33-46fa-b09a-2369d0b124a2', 30, 217, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original//xPXDVhVKt0XM34ihoUVMHtLYTw8.jpg', '▫️Short review: Twisted, dark, and suffused with heavy depression— these are perhaps the most precise adjectives to describe “Takopi”. The film penetrates deeply into the psychology of its characters. It keeps viewers in awe, unsettled by the characters’ motives and the haunting uncertainty of what will unfold next. This film is by no means suitable for children.\n\n▫️Rating • Plot: 9.8 • Twist 9.5 • Characters: 9.8 • Animation: 9.0 • Pacing: 9.0 • Music/OST:8.8\n▫️Overal: 9.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Takopi’s Original Sin', 'Anime (+18)', 'Akyl_Lee/10207441-2d33-46fa-b09a-2369d0b124a2', 4.7, '2025-08-17 13:55:32', '2025-08-17 13:55:32'),
('15d5a76f-8d9b-46b4-a291-3aad10840f2c', 40, 217, 'https://rapchieuphim.com/photos/9/tham-tu-kien.jpg', '▫️Short review: Victor Vu returns to his signature genre, with this one transporting us into a majestic natural landscape infused with the timeless beauty of Vietnamese villages. Regardless of promising screenplay, it falls short in delivering the investigative depth of true detective genre. Leaving hope for a comeback as impactful as Scandal.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 6.8 • Twist: 6.5 • Acting: 7.3 • Cine: 8.5 • Pacing: 6.5 • VFX: 7.8 \n• Make up & Hairstyling :8.0 • Music: 6.8 \n▫️Overall: 7.2 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Detective Kien: The Headless Horror', 'Folk Horror/Mystery', 'Akyl_Lee/15d5a76f-8d9b-46b4-a291-3aad10840f2c', 3.6, '2025-08-23 08:20:06', '2025-08-23 08:20:06'),
('17312adb-6ed0-460f-bde0-a2cfbb47ed89', 56, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/pv-target-images/fdf4e6d9aaf30b73c4754791079fd804740ab33c2f25bc568440555783d0774f.jpg', '▫️Short review: Orphan (2009) subverts conventional horror tropes by combining psychological tension with a shocking narrative twist. Isabelle Fuhrman’s chilling performance as Esther elevates the film beyond its genre trappings, while the carefully crafted suspense sustains audience engagement.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 8.5 • Twist: 9.0 • Message: 6.8\n• Acting: 10 • Cine: 7.0 • Pacing: 8.8\n• MU&H: 8.7\n• Music: 7.0▫️Overall: 8.2 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Orphan (2009)', 'Thriller', 'Akyl_Lee/17312adb-6ed0-460f-bde0-a2cfbb47ed89', 4.1, '2025-09-06 08:16:10', '2025-09-06 08:16:10'),
('1801c8fa-d555-4fbe-a0be-0aef52dadba2', 20, 215, 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/nightjarprod/content/uploads/sites/130/2025/06/11093142/ombsmhYUqR4qqOLOxAyr5V8hbyv-scaled.jpg', '▫️Rating\n • Plot: 9.0 • Twist 8.0 • Acting: 7.8 • Cinematography: 9.5 • Pacing: 10 • Visual effect: 9.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 9.0 • Music/OST: 9.0 \n\n▫️Overal: 9.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️) \n\n▫️Short review: Never doubting about James Gunn. He brought us his best work on this new Superman. I absolutely was stunned while watching this. The visual and cinematography are staggering. David Corenswet unmistakably carries the aura of a Superman figure in the way this character is portrayed.', 'Superman 2025', 'Film', 'Akyl_ee/1801c8fa-d555-4fbe-a0be-0aef52dadba2', 4.5, '2025-08-17 01:57:15', '2025-08-17 01:57:15'),
('18f9722a-86dc-45d8-a302-a1bd70dbb3f9', 51, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51PHxyy0R1L.jpg', '▫️Short review: Haunting, harrowing, dark, and singularly disturbing—Hereditary terrifies without resorting to cheap jump scares. Its unconventional storytelling and unrelenting tension culminate in scenes of unbearable intensity. Anchored by the electrifying performances, especially Toni Collette’s tour de force—an Oscar-worthy portrayal of unhinged brilliance.', 'Hereditary (2018)', 'Supernatural Horror', 'Akyl_Lee/18f9722a-86dc-45d8-a302-a1bd70dbb3f9', 5.0, '2025-08-27 09:34:39', '2025-08-27 09:34:39'),
('1b0ad955-4dea-4fb7-87ab-ffac2035bbd5', 65, 217, 'https://www.cgv.vn/media/catalog/product/cache/3/image/c5f0a1eff4c394a251036189ccddaacd/r/s/rsz_chkm8_001a_fpo.jpg', '▫️Short review: Genuinely and perfectly stunning in every frame. Great storyline and breathtaking world-building. Never been into magic stuff but after watching this, my mind changed due to its awesomeness. Dr.Strange also has a deep and meaningful message on the philosophy of life. ▫️Rating • Plot: 10 • Twist 9.0 • Acting: 8.5\n • Cinematography: 10 • Pacing: 9.0 • VFX: 10\n • Make up and hairstyling: 10 • Music/OST: 9.0 ▫️Overall: 9.3 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Doctor Strange • 2016', 'MCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/1b0ad955-4dea-4fb7-87ab-ffac2035bbd5', 4.6, '2025-11-25 12:54:39', '2025-11-25 12:54:39'),
