('3174a372-7aa2-4224-8944-1f0f1d767e21', 56, 217, 'https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/f/eafb5739-e9db-4a02-bc09-9b88be835ea5/di70tne-4fa04523-1622-4961-a2aa-65fa1b8273f2.jpg/v1/fit/w_828,h_1226,q_70,strp/agatha_all_along___poster_7_by_iconuser123_di70tne-414w-2x.jpg?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..9IMZtp2zCYV8wqYHdpXzweaDAdRUfnXs4PSqcjNBoF4', '▫️Short review: A spellbinding world of magic—haunting, alluring, and full of surprises. Agatha All Along shatters all prior doubts with a screenplay that is both masterful and layered. Viewers are drawn as if under enchantment, only to be jolted by the film’s startling turns. ▫️Rating • Plot: 10 \n• Twist: 10 • Message: 8.5 • Acting: 9.5 \n• Cinematography: 8.8 • Pacing: 8.0 \n• Make up and hairstyling: 10 \n• Music: 10▫️Overall: 9.1 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Agatha All Along (2024)', 'MCU | 🔝10 TV Series', 'Akyl_Lee/3174a372-7aa2-4224-8944-1f0f1d767e21', 4.5, '2025-09-05 12:01:41', '2025-09-05 12:01:41'),
