('36c63450-a26e-4804-ac79-4664a942857e', 65, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71pAwt4KT6L._AC_UF894,1000_QL80_.jpg', '▫️Short review: Moon Knight is a distinctive superhero work, blending psychological complexity with mythological intrigue, elevated by Oscar Isaac’s remarkable performance. Though its narrative lacks full cohesion, the series stands as a bold and singular experiment within the MCU. \n▫️Rating • Plot: 9.5 • Twist: 9.0\n• Message: 8.0 • Acting: 10 • Cinematography: 8.8 \n• Pacing: 7.8 • Make up and hairstyling: 10 \n• Music: 9.5 ▫️Overall: 9.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Moon Knight • 2022', 'MCU • TV Series | 🔝 10 Series', 'Akyl_Lee/36c63450-a26e-4804-ac79-4664a942857e', 4.5, '2025-11-24 12:21:27', '2025-11-24 12:21:27'),
('38ae56f7-0bc8-4035-adab-0f759bee8c05', 34, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTM3NjA1NDMyMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDQzNDMzOQ@@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_.jpg', '▫️Short review: The Conjuring”  is an outstanding horror film that delivers fear through tense atmosphere and tight storytelling. James Wan avoids cheap jump scares, instead building suspense with sound, visuals, and performances. It successfully revives the classic spirit of supernatural horror. This is also the best one in the franchise.', 'The Conjuring (2013)', 'Supernatural Horror', 'Akyl_Lee/38ae56f7-0bc8-4035-adab-0f759bee8c05', 5.0, '2025-09-04 10:34:13', '2025-09-04 10:34:13'),
('38d58f04-6349-4ab4-89e5-5f6bcbefb2a9', 62, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61EH4imxyjL._UF1000,1000_QL80_.jpg', '▫️Short review: Attack on Titan is a genre-defining masterpiece—ambitious, brutal, and unforgettable and a landmark anime that transcends the boundaries of its genre. What begins as a dark fantasy survival story about humanity fighting against monstrous Titans evolves into a sprawling, morally complex epic about freedom, oppression, war, and the cyclical nature of hatred.', 'Attack On Titan | 2013-2023', 'Anime • TV Series | C16', 'Akyl_Lee/38d58f04-6349-4ab4-89e5-5f6bcbefb2a9', 5.0, '2025-09-27 15:24:52', '2025-09-27 15:24:52'),
('3dedf148-7671-4c67-beba-74c211193ccb', 49, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMWU3Y2NlZmEtMjJjNS00ZWMxLWE1MzctYWYyMjMzMDdkNTE4XkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_.jpg', '▫️Short review: Insane, funny, surprising, and eccentric. James Gunn has delivered a perfect version of The Suicide Squad, capturing exactly the ‘madness’ of this outrageous team of supervillain misfits.\n▫️Rating: \n• Plot: 8.5 • Twist: 7.8 • Acting: 8.0\n • Cinematography: 8.0 • Pacing: 9.5\n • VFX: 9.8 • Make up and hairstyling: 8.8 \n• Music/OST: 7.5\n▫️Overall: 8.4 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'The Suicide Squad (2021)', 'DCU', 'Akyl_Lee/3dedf148-7671-4c67-beba-74c211193ccb', 4.2, '2025-08-25 07:24:53', '2025-08-25 07:24:53'),
('3e304556-1bff-44d1-bca0-74b0b8f3304b', 47, 217, 'https://i0.wp.com/www.impawards.com/2009/posters/avatar_xlg.jpg', '▫️Short review: An otherworldly experience that is beyond imagination, Avatar feels like a cinematic masterpiece sent from the future—unbelievable for 2009, when digital filmmaking had yet to peak. Every frame unfolds like a marvel, a vivid chronicle of Pandora’s grandeur and wonder, as if documenting a real, living world. Despite an imperfect script, Avatar endures as a once-in-a-lifetime masterpiece, retaining its resonance for more than two decades.', 'Avatar (2009)', 'Sci-Fi/Fantasy', 'Akyl_Lee/3e304556-1bff-44d1-bca0-74b0b8f3304b', 5.0, '2025-08-28 14:40:46', '2025-08-28 14:40:46'),
