('3fd27a3e-5eaf-4377-bf5b-8036939cd540', 41, 217, 'https://occ-0-8407-92.1.nflxso.net/dnm/api/v6/Z-WHgqd_TeJxSuha8aZ5WpyLcX8/AAAABczqmz9poohqTHaRiuRL3Xh97tB9OoxyUbxdV2X_hvqK30xpbcjy6L9MGlKL-erP4Jr0inHdQVQwJkCVlgdVnxyoKnmE_J5vv02v.jpg?r=905', '▫️Short review: Twisted, dark, and suffused with heavy depression— these are perhaps the most precise adjectives to describe “Takopi”. The film penetrates deeply into the psychology of its characters. It keeps viewers in awe, unsettled by the characters’ motives and the haunting uncertainty of what will unfold next. ▫️Rating • Plot: 9.8 • Twist: 9.5 • Message: 10 • Characters: 9.8 • Animation: 9.0 • Pacing: 9.0 • Music/OST: 8.8 ▫️Overal: 9.4 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Takopi’s Original Sin', 'Anime | T18', 'Akyl_Lee/3fd27a3e-5eaf-4377-bf5b-8036939cd540', 4.7, '2025-08-20 03:16:42', '2025-08-20 03:16:42'),
