('44a2b86b-0897-4f27-a178-a3734e7414d8', 76, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODY2MTAzOTQ4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzg5MTE0MjI@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_.jpg', '▫️Short review: A refreshing new beginning, though not without its shortcomings. Marvel has dressed Spider-Man in a high-school spirit—youthful, energetic, and vibrant. Yet the script falls slightly short in exploring the depth of Peter Parker, as portrayed by Tom Holland, while the film itself lacks both surprising turns and a truly impactful climax. ▫️Rating • Plot: 7.5 • Twist: 6.8 • Message: 7.8 • Acting: 8.0 • Cine: 8.6 • Pacing: 8.8\n • MU&H:7.8 •VFX: 8.4 • Music: 7.0▫️Overall: 7.8 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Spider-Man: Homecoming', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/44a2b86b-0897-4f27-a178-a3734e7414d8', 3.9, '2025-12-11 22:22:52', '2025-12-11 22:22:52'),
