('4aea01ba-648a-4a17-91b6-a7ec4ff1671b', 48, 217, 'https://cdn.marvel.com/content/1x/loki_season_2.jpg', '▫️Short review: Loki embodies Marvel’s artistic ambition on television: a story both philosophical and emotional, transforming a familiar villain beyond the confines of superhero tropes into an epic tragedy that is at once grand and profoundly human.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 10 • Twist: 9.5 • Message: 9.0 • Acting: 9.0 • Cinematography: 9.4 • Pacing: 8.2 • Make up and hairstyling: 8.9 •VFX: 9.5\n• Music: 9.0▫️Overall: 9.1 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Loki (2021-2023)', 'MCU | 🔝10 TV Series', 'Akyl_Lee/4aea01ba-648a-4a17-91b6-a7ec4ff1671b', 4.6, '2025-09-01 09:44:07', '2025-09-01 09:44:07'),
