('5ccdac5a-7aba-4bb8-9aa0-7280e8cb6a39', 37, 217, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original//xPXDVhVKt0XM34ihoUVMHtLYTw8.jpg', '▫️Short review: Twisted, dark, and suffused with heavy depression— these are perhaps the most precise adjectives to describe “Takopi”. The film penetrates deeply into the psychology of its characters. It keeps viewers in awe, unsettled by the characters’ motives and the haunting uncertainty of what will unfold next. This film is by no means suitable for children. \n\n▫️Rating • Plot: 9.8 • Twist: 9.5 • Characters: 9.8 \n  • Animation: 9.0 • Pacing: 9.0 • Music/OST: 8.8 ▫️Overal: 9.4 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Takopi’s Original Sin', 'Anime | T18', 'Akyl_Lee/5ccdac5a-7aba-4bb8-9aa0-7280e8cb6a39', 4.7, '2025-08-17 14:03:20', '2025-08-17 14:03:20'),
('5d421a84-6b27-4d2b-acda-024cfe529df0', 60, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61EH4imxyjL._UF1000,1000_QL80_.jpg', '▫️Short review: Attack on Titan is a genre-defining masterpiece—ambitious, brutal, and unforgettable. What begins as a dark fantasy survival story about humanity fighting against monstrous Titans evolves into a sprawling, morally complex epic about freedom, oppression, war, and the cyclical nature of hatred.', 'Attack On Titan • [2013-2023]', 'Anime • TV Series | C16', 'Akyl_Lee/5d421a84-6b27-4d2b-acda-024cfe529df0', 5.0, '2025-09-27 15:17:12', '2025-09-27 15:17:12'),
('5e219f4b-8d65-45ac-a722-7ce0e748df45', 49, 217, 'https://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/6V4AAOSwOZlnY6Rv/s-l1200.jpg', '▫️Short review: Never doubting about James Gunn. He brought us his best work on this new Superman. I absolutely was stunned while watching this. The visual and cinematography are staggering. David Corenswet unmistakably carries the aura of a Superman figure in the way this character is portrayed. ▫️Rating • Plot: 9.0 • Twist 8.0 • Message: 9.0 • Acting: 7.8 • Cinematography: 9.5 • Pacing: 10 • Visual effect: 9.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 9.0 • Music/OST: 9.0 ▫️Overall: 9.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Superman (2025)', 'DCU', 'Akyl_Lee/5e219f4b-8d65-45ac-a722-7ce0e748df45', 4.5, '2025-08-25 07:07:37', '2025-08-25 07:07:37'),
('5e780a8e-16f0-4e4d-9709-32fd38da4859', 52, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZTlhYTk1ZTEtOWY3NC00NWQ5LTlkOTctNjQ3ZDYyZGE5ZWNlXkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_.jpg', '▫️Short review: I would be lying if I said I didn’t expect something more explosive from Bring Her Back after its gripping trailers. The film’s restraint from cheap jump-scares, instead probing the audience’s psyche through character motivation. Moments of surprise, suffocation intensify the viewing experience, making it feel all the more authentic.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 7.8 • Twist: 7.0 • Message: 8.0 • Acting: 8.0 • Cine: 8.4 • Pacing: 8.8 • VFX: 7.5\n• MU&H: 7.8 • Music: 7.0\n▫️Overall: 7.8 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Bring Her Back (2025)', 'Supernatural Horror', 'Akyl_Lee/5e780a8e-16f0-4e4d-9709-32fd38da4859', 3.9, '2025-08-28 10:19:51', '2025-08-28 10:19:51');
INSERT INTO `vibe_others` (`id`, `category_other_id`, `user_id`, `image_url`, `comment`, `title`, `desc`, `path`, `rating`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
('5f4de7b4-72e3-4414-bd37-5fdb92e9cb9a', 76, 217, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/marvels-guardians-of-the-galaxy/images/a/ab/Key_art.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/1200?cb=20211025013751', 'Vibrant, funny, heartfelt, GOTG Vol. 1 delivers a sharp and engaging take on the superhero ensemble genre. The film blends humor, emotion, and style to portray a group of misfits forming an unexpected family. With its lively visuals and iconic soundtrack, it remains both entertaining and thoughtfully crafted.\n▫️Rate: • Plot: 9.0\n• Twist: 8.0\n• Acting: 8.5\n• Cinematography: 9.0\n• Pacing: 8.8\n• Visual Effect: 9.5\n• Make-up & Hairstyling: 8.5\n• Music/OST: 9.5\n\n▫️ Overall: 8.8 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Guardians of the Galaxy Vol.1', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/5f4de7b4-72e3-4414-bd37-5fdb92e9cb9a', 4.4, '2025-12-12 10:23:24', '2025-12-12 10:23:24'),
('621716b1-c05b-4faf-83f7-f23953e443f4', 72, 217, 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/nightjarprod/content/uploads/sites/130/2024/03/29150816/7IiTTgloJzvGI1TAYymCfbfl3vT-scaled.jpg', '▫️Short review: A remarkable cinematic masterpiece of the 21st century, Parasite embraces the full range of human emotions—joy, humor, tension, anxiety, and an ineffable melancholy. With a masterfully crafted script and a searing commentary on class divisions in Korean society, Bong Joon Ho delivers a film that overwhelms the mind and leaves audiences awestruck, lingering in silent astonishment through its final moments.', 'Parasite (2019)', 'Drama/Dark Comedy', 'Akyl_Lee/621716b1-c05b-4faf-83f7-f23953e443f4', 5.0, '2025-12-02 10:22:28', '2025-12-02 10:22:28'),
('6a01d095-ee9b-4afd-b2d9-4d1fbbbdc413', 56, 217, 'https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/f/0edd837b-eb3c-42fd-8f32-9a04c89d1619/d78e7b0-ed1bdd88-a2f3-4259-82d1-c8b83d843364.jpg/v1/fit/w_828,h_1158,q_70,strp/captain_america__the_winter_soldier_by_phetvanburton_d78e7b0-414w-2x.jpg?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..3pRl-ZAKV1WRDRGLJV63SVOBzJOxSdboWmiOe1N949I', '▫️Short review: A superhero film of absolute perfection, Captain America: The Winter Soldier balances politics and action with precision. Its spectacular, gripping fight sequences and tightly crafted, layered script have made it the benchmark for MCU films in the years that followed.', 'Captain America: The Winter Soldier', 'MCU | 🔝10 Movies', 'Akyl_Lee/6a01d095-ee9b-4afd-b2d9-4d1fbbbdc413', 5.0, '2025-09-05 06:59:59', '2025-09-05 06:59:59'),
('6b3b07f0-ec39-463b-b9d2-c2a8d3cd8da1', 52, 217, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/ulBLIBqvdnf4H6JBt0OpMCU1ECn.jpg', '▫️Short review: Disturbing & unsettling. The film deeply explores violence born from isolation and unfulfilled ambition. Avoiding conventional scares, instead creating tension through performance and visual contrast between its bright aesthetic and Pearl’s mental decline. Anchored by Mia Goth’s controlled and compelling acting.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 8.0 • Twist: 6.0 • Message: 6.8 \n• Acting: 9.7 • Cine: 8.8 • Pacing: 8.0 • MU&H: 8.9 \n• Music: 7.8\n▫️Overall: 8.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Pearl (2022)', 'Psychological Thriller', 'Akyl_Lee/6b3b07f0-ec39-463b-b9d2-c2a8d3cd8da1', 4.0, '2025-12-15 10:05:38', '2025-12-15 10:05:38'),
('6d8e388f-f83a-40b6-b9b3-6392ddcf5efc', 76, 217, 'https://mir-s3-cdn-cf.behance.net/project_modules/hd/0dfbbd79079049.5cb7d6792ef30.jpg', '▫️Short review: Avengers: Endgame” stands as a cinematic epic that concludes over a decade of Marvel storytelling. It masterfully balances cosmic spectacle with profound emotional resonance, delivering both grandeur and intimacy. Despite minor flaws in pacing and time-travel logic, the film endures as a historic milestone in the superhero genre.', 'Avengers: Endgame', 'MCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/6d8e388f-f83a-40b6-b9b3-6392ddcf5efc', 5.0, '2025-12-11 22:55:04', '2025-12-11 22:55:04'),
('6e553915-9577-4fe7-88d7-954643ef8ecc', 48, 217, 'https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/f/eafb5739-e9db-4a02-bc09-9b88be835ea5/di70tne-4fa04523-1622-4961-a2aa-65fa1b8273f2.jpg/v1/fit/w_828,h_1226,q_70,strp/agatha_all_along___poster_7_by_iconuser123_di70tne-414w-2x.jpg?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..9IMZtp2zCYV8wqYHdpXzweaDAdRUfnXs4PSqcjNBoF4', '▫️Short review: A spellbinding world of magic—haunting, alluring, and full of surprises. Agatha All Along shatters all prior doubts with a screenplay that is both masterful and layered. Viewers are drawn as if under enchantment, only to be jolted by the film’s startling turns.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 10 • Twist: 10 • Message: 8.5 • Acting: 9.5 • Cinematography: 8.8 • Pacing: 8.0 \n• Make up and hairstyling: 10\n• Music: 10▫️Overall: 9.1 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Agatha All Along', 'MCU | 🔝10 TV Series', 'Akyl_Lee/6e553915-9577-4fe7-88d7-954643ef8ecc', 4.6, '2025-09-01 09:17:42', '2025-09-01 09:17:42'),
('6ee8529f-e105-436e-abd6-35028205ac15', 40, 217, 'https://thethaovanhoa.mediacdn.vn/2012/10/04/09/45/POSTER-SCANDAL.jpg', '▫️Short review: One of the most excellent film of Victor Vu, Scandal guides viewers into the darkest recesses of showbiz, where envy and the blind pursuit of fame consume its characters, only to leave the audiences stunned by its unexpected twists.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 9.5 • Twist: 10 • Message: 6.8 \n• Acting: 10 • Cinematography: 8.5 • Pacing: 8.0\n • Visual effect: 7.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 8.5\n • Music/OST: 7.0▫️Overall: 8.3 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Scandal (2012)', 'Thriller/Mystery', 'Akyl_Lee/6ee8529f-e105-436e-abd6-35028205ac15', 4.1, '2025-08-24 09:18:13', '2025-08-24 09:18:13'),
('6f524a9f-67d4-48f9-a437-f9effb4784c2', 47, 217, 'https://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/ZYkAAOSwbiFZW6oA/s-l1200.jpg', '▫️Short review: Breathtaking, striking, and visually explosive, with a narrative that transcends the imagination of its era— Inception rightfully stands as one of Christopher Nolan’s towering masterpieces of the past two decades.', 'Inception (2010)', 'Sci-Fi', 'Akyl_Lee/6f524a9f-67d4-48f9-a437-f9effb4784c2', 5.0, '2025-08-23 06:38:54', '2025-08-23 06:38:54'),
('6f5a6920-792c-48aa-a82c-4a13858e24c8', 3, 6, 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTUU_tb5aBO5OfzhsIStnkD67OKQPcfdwIAL7h81rg3yDT1JbkSkofH154&s=10', 'Why he mad at everyone', 'Eye of Rah', 'Rashad Bowens', 'luker_feller/6f5a6920-792c-48aa-a82c-4a13858e24c8', 5.0, '2025-03-03 01:05:28', '2025-03-03 01:05:28'),
('70abcd81-211c-49c3-bf46-513c5bb31dd6', 65, 217, 'https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/f/4b4d6e0f-04fe-49ac-a8c8-ca6e8024a16f/deqhy0d-fd9a03e5-6c62-49ad-ad68-35daa481bdf6.jpg?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..vXgE3n8pB29kr1O9G7hBP8qOt3pjLI-A9g_ntKpNHQk', '▫️Short review: As one of the first Asian superheroes to debut in the MCU, Shang-Chi dazzles with kinetic martial arts and a mythic, Eastern-tinged narrative - securing its place among the top 10 Marvel titles not to be missed. ▫️Rating: • Plot: 8.0 • Twist: 7.0 • Message: 8.0 \n• Acting: 7.5 • Cinematography: 8.8 • Pacing: 10 \n• Visual effect: 7.9 • Make up & hairstyling: 8.0 \n• Music/OST: 8.8 ▫️Overall: 8.2 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings • 2021', 'MCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/70abcd81-211c-49c3-bf46-513c5bb31dd6', 4.1, '2025-11-23 11:13:00', '2025-11-23 11:13:00'),
('71e9beb6-cc13-4898-82e7-101c11f07796', 46, 217, 'https://cdn.tgdd.vn//GameApp/-1//review-phim-inception-ke-danh-cap-giac-mo-1-800x1200.jpg', 'Breathtaking, striking, and visually explosive, with a narrative that transcends the imagination of its era— Inception rightfully stands as one of Christopher Nolan’s towering masterpieces of the past two decades.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 10 • Twist: 10 • Message: 10 • Acting: 10 • Cinematography: 10 • Pacing: 10 • Visual effect: 10 • Make up and hairstyling: 10 • Music / OST: 10▫️Overall: 10 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Inception (2010)', 'Sci-Fi', 'Akyl_Lee/71e9beb6-cc13-4898-82e7-101c11f07796', 5.0, '2025-08-22 09:05:12', '2025-08-22 09:05:12'),
('75811171-550e-410d-88d1-672d98306b15', 20, 215, 'https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Gq6MS4ZWAAAFj7a.jpg:large', '▫️Rating \n\n• Plot: 9.0 • Twist 8.0 • Acting: 7.8 • Cinematography: 9.5 • Pacing: 10 • Visual effect: 9.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 9.0 • Music/OST: 9.0 \n\n\n▫️Overal: 9.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)\n\n\n▫️Short review: Never doubting about James Gunn. He brought us his best work on this new Superman. I absolutely was stunned while watching this. The visual and cinematography are staggering. David Corenswet unmistakably carries the aura of a Superman figure in the way this character is portrayed.', 'Superman 2025', 'Film', 'Akyl_ee/75811171-550e-410d-88d1-672d98306b15', 4.5, '2025-08-17 02:08:41', '2025-08-17 02:08:41'),
('758cfe3d-ccd1-4ab5-9253-8050ff41c61a', 74, 217, 'https://avatars.mds.yandex.net/get-kinopoisk-image/1599028/e6f3f6c8-032c-43af-8d25-26e35e53e87e/1080x', '▫️Short review: A superhero film of absolute perfection, Captain America: The Winter Soldier balances politics and action with precision. Its spectacular, gripping fight sequences and tightly crafted, layered script have made it the benchmark for MCU films in the years that followed.', 'Captain America: The Winter Soldier', 'MCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/758cfe3d-ccd1-4ab5-9253-8050ff41c61a', 5.0, '2025-12-08 12:01:11', '2025-12-08 12:01:11'),
('75c35017-bde2-4c9b-83a8-8ba3a2f34f10', 38, 217, 'https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/91ckLZfJiBL.jpg', '▫️Short review: A perfect entry point for anime newbies, it awakens every sense of audience with its breathtaking visuals and vibrant soundscape. Its story is meticulously crafted—captivating and surprising in every detail—while the OST amplifies its sense of wonder. \n▫️Rating • Plot: 9.5 • Twist: 9.0 • Characters: 9.0 • Animation: 10 • Pacing: 10 • Visual effect: 10\n • Music/OST: 10 ▫️Overal: 9.8 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Your Name (2016)', 'Anime/Fantasy/Romance', 'Akyl_Lee/75c35017-bde2-4c9b-83a8-8ba3a2f34f10', 4.8, '2025-08-19 09:07:09', '2025-08-19 09:07:09'),
('75d7e3b4-4c82-4adb-9fe3-36c43d37d835', 36, 217, 'https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/501b147ae4b07cab1f91ea20/1565868487974-XLGDXMMJLAKH9EC2AAB3/spiderman-small.jpg', 'Loeve', 'Far from', 'Mcu', 'Akyl_Lee/75d7e3b4-4c82-4adb-9fe3-36c43d37d835', 4.7, '2025-08-31 11:09:24', '2025-08-31 11:09:24'),
('76cc71f3-e86d-44ad-aeb5-27aa7019de80', 56, 217, 'https://static1.squarespace.com/static/51b3dc8ee4b051b96ceb10de/51ce6099e4b0d911b4489b79/556a87dce4b03fe792a7a5ed/1557985660937/?format=1500w', '▫️Short review: Though not the MCU’s finest, Ant-Man hold a place in top 10 MCU films IMO. It presents an unusual hero with a quirky power and a troubled background. This conflict leaves audiences to question what truly defines a hero. ▫️Rating • Plot: 8.8 • Twist: 7.0 • Message: 6.5\n • Acting: 7.7 • Cinematography: 8.0 • Pacing: 7.9 \n• VFX: 9.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 7.0 • Music: 8.0▫️Overall: 7.7(⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Ant-Man (2015)', 'MCU | 🔝10 Movies', 'Akyl_Lee/76cc71f3-e86d-44ad-aeb5-27aa7019de80', 3.8, '2025-09-05 08:06:50', '2025-09-05 08:06:50'),
('780ee610-6f2b-4ce7-9a34-6d0726bf9413', 76, 217, 'https://avatars.mds.yandex.net/get-kinopoisk-image/6201401/c837fe6f-0c5b-459e-8b6d-2c10b56718b2/1080x', '▫️Short review: Moon Knight is a distinctive superhero work, blending psychological complexity with mythological intrigue, elevated by Oscar Isaac’s remarkable performance. Though its narrative lacks full cohesion, the series stands as a bold and singular experiment within the MCU. ▫️Rating • Plot: 9.5 • Twist: 9.0 \n• Message: 8.0 • Acting: 10 • Cinematography: 8.8\n • Pacing: 7.8 • Make up and hairstyling: 10 • Music: 9.5 ▫️Overall: 9.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Moon Knight (2022)', 'MCU • TV Series | 🔝 10 Series', 'Akyl_Lee/780ee610-6f2b-4ce7-9a34-6d0726bf9413', 4.5, '2025-12-08 12:54:45', '2025-12-08 12:54:45'),
('7a4e0b43-e214-4cf1-a990-e354c5b72563', 56, 217, 'https://mir-s3-cdn-cf.behance.net/project_modules/1400/51aff3146743841.62b595ba09230.jpg', '▫️Short review: As one of the first Asian superheroes to debut in the MCU, Shang-Chi dazzles with kinetic martial arts and a mythic, Eastern-tinged narrative - securing its place among the top 10 Marvel titles not to be missed. ▫️Rating: • Plot: 8.0 • Twist: 7.0 • Message: 8.0 \n• Acting: 7.5 • Cinematography: 8.8 • Pacing: 10 \n• Visual effect: 7.9 • Make up & hairstyling: 8.0\n • Music/OST: 8.8 \n▫️Overall: 8.2 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings', 'MCU | 🔝10 Movies', 'Akyl_Lee/7a4e0b43-e214-4cf1-a990-e354c5b72563', 4.1, '2025-09-05 11:20:19', '2025-09-05 11:20:19'),
('7d5efed6-6136-4ed2-afea-c04c168fdc2d', 34, 217, 'https://bazaarvietnam.vn/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ke-dong-hanh-companion-khi-ban-gai-robot-noi-loan-3.jpg', '▫️Short review: Surprisingly and unexpectedly fresh, it reinvents the familiar story line of artificial intelligence with humor, creative, clever, and striking effectiveness.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 8.8 • Twist: 7.0 • Message: 8.0 • Acting: 8.0 • Cinematography: 7.8 • Pacing: 8.0 • Visual effect: 7.5 • Make up and hairstyling: 9.0 • Music / OST: 7.0 ▫️Overall: 7.9 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Companion (2025)', 'Thriller/Dark Comedy', 'Akyl_Lee/7d5efed6-6136-4ed2-afea-c04c168fdc2d', 3.9, '2025-08-22 09:30:28', '2025-08-22 09:30:28'),
('7fe7e5db-195a-48cf-82bf-3ee4cb8b7ccc', 56, 217, 'https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/f/0bb0dd0f-3a24-48e3-83a5-b476ca307a1f/dk4aq7w-0191805f-c37c-49ef-9364-179a5d795a2a.jpg/v1/fill/w_1280,h_2276,q_75,strp/the_fantastic_four__first_steps__2025___wallpaper_by_chamikanlakshan_dk4aq7w-fullview.jpg?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..WIyamWeZQEdXhcMgI36mDsC1I0GNfNueV34m5XsPLYE', 'Short review: A sigh of relief accompanies the long-awaited return of Fantastic Four to its rightful path after past failures. Galactus appears in true grandeur, not just a silly cloud. “The black hole” scene truly astounds, though some CGI falters. The credits add a clever final note. ▫️Rating: • Plot: 8.0 • Twist: 7.0 • Acting: 8.0\n • Cinematography: 9.0 • Pacing: 7.6 • Visual effect: 7.5 • Make up & hairstyling: 9.0 • Music/OST: 8.8\n • Message: 7.0 ▫️Overall: 7.7. (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'The Fantastic Four: First Steps', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/7fe7e5db-195a-48cf-82bf-3ee4cb8b7ccc', 3.8, '2025-09-05 07:43:10', '2025-09-05 07:43:10'),
('82b7018e-1c44-40be-baec-417d144809b5', 34, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTY3NzIyNTA2NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNzE2NjI4Nw@@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_.jpg', '▫️Short review: Visually stunning and thematically ambitious,  blending cosmic horror with existential inquiry. R.Scott crafts a haunting atmosphere, supported by striking cine and state-of-the-art VFX. While the script leaves certain questions unresolved, its exploration of creation, faith, and human fragility elevates it beyond conventional genre fare.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 8.5 • Twist: 7.8 • Mess: 7.5 \n• Acting: 8.5 • Cine: 9.2 • Pacing: 8.8 \n• MU&H: 10 •VFX: 10\n• Music: 8.4 ▫Overall: 8.4 (⭐⭐️⭐⭐️)', 'Prometheus (2012)', 'Sci-fi Horror [AF]', 'Akyl_Lee/82b7018e-1c44-40be-baec-417d144809b5', 4.3, '2025-09-04 12:04:31', '2025-09-04 12:04:31'),
