('a2114a8f-ee63-4fb1-9a01-43bc6fd275df', 76, 217, 'https://avatars.mds.yandex.net/get-kinopoisk-image/6201401/0c6cf88f-7a39-4627-9a5d-630ad4c40e9e/1080x', '▫️Short review: Loki embodies Marvel’s artistic ambition on television: a story both philosophical and emotional, transforming a familiar villain beyond the confines of superhero tropes into an epic tragedy that is at once grand and profoundly human. ▫️Rating • Plot: 10 • Twist: 9.5 \n• Message: 9.0 • Acting: 9.0 • Cinematography: 9.4 • Pacing: 8.2 • Make up and hairstyling: 8.9 •VFX: 9.5 • Music: 9.0▫️Overall: 9.1 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Loki [2SS] (2021-2023)', 'MCU • TV Series | 🔝 10 Series', 'Akyl_Lee/a2114a8f-ee63-4fb1-9a01-43bc6fd275df', 4.5, '2025-12-11 08:55:19', '2025-12-11 08:55:19'),
('a507449e-fe25-4180-814e-457c461b74e6', 47, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjJhNTYxOGUtYWQxMS00YjYwLWFmMWItOWViN2QyZmZhNDM3XkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_.jpg', '▫️Short review: Genuinely unique- a thrilling and unparalleled experience. Under Baz Poonpiriya’s direction, the schoolyard theme comes to life with unprecedented vibrancy and allure. A tightly crafted script, charged with suspense, surprising twists, and profound message.', 'Bad Genius (2017)', 'Crime/Drama', 'Akyl_Lee/a507449e-fe25-4180-814e-457c461b74e6', 5.0, '2025-08-25 23:34:12', '2025-08-25 23:34:12'),
('a60cc8af-7587-49a3-8168-099cdf06283a', 72, 217, 'https://avatars.mds.yandex.net/get-kinopoisk-image/1773646/38fe18da-d418-45bc-998d-55115924ec19/1080x', '▫️Short review: An otherworldly experience that is beyond imagination, Avatar feels like a cinematic masterpiece sent from the future—unbelievable for 2009, when digital filmmaking had yet to peak. Every frame unfolds like a marvel, a vivid chronicle of Pandora’s grandeur and wonder, as if documenting a real, living world. Despite an imperfect script, Avatar endures as a once-in-a-lifetime masterpiece, retaining its resonance for more than two decades.', 'Avatar (2009)', 'Sci-Fi/Fantasy', 'Akyl_Lee/a60cc8af-7587-49a3-8168-099cdf06283a', 5.0, '2025-12-06 11:27:41', '2025-12-06 11:27:41'),
('a8b93ea0-b335-46e6-943f-120487ef2b1a', 56, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODY2MTAzOTQ4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzg5MTE0MjI@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_.jpg', '▫️Short review: A refreshing new beginning, though not without its shortcomings. Marvel has dressed Spider-Man in a high-school spirit—youthful, energetic, and vibrant. Yet the script falls slightly short in exploring the depth of Peter Parker, as portrayed by Tom Holland, while the film itself lacks both surprising turns and a truly impactful climax.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 7.5 • Twist: 6.8 • Message: 7.8\n• Acting: 8.0 • Cine: 8.6 • Pacing: 8.8\n• MU&H:7.8 •VFX: 8.4\n• Music: 7.0▫️Overall: 7.8 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Spider-Man: Homecoming', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/a8b93ea0-b335-46e6-943f-120487ef2b1a', 3.9, '2025-09-05 13:18:26', '2025-09-05 13:18:26'),
('b2663806-f405-4982-84d4-8fba2a13d67f', 24, 217, 'https://imagedelivery.net/c2SKP8Bk0ZKw6UDgeeIlbw/5cdbb576-6b2e-4ba1-13df-aca42cc83400/public', '▫️Short review: Never doubting about James Gunn. He brought us his best work on this new Superman. I absolutely was stunned while watching this. The visual and cinematography are staggering. David Corenswet unmistakably carries the aura of a Superman figure in the way this character is portrayed.\n\n▫️Rating • Plot: 9.0 • Twist 8.0 • Acting: 7.8 • Cinematography: 9.5 • Pacing: 10 • Visual effect: 9.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 9.0 • Music/OST: 9.0 ▫️Overal: 9.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Superman 2025', 'DCU', 'Akyl_Lee/b2663806-f405-4982-84d4-8fba2a13d67f', 4.5, '2025-08-17 12:54:50', '2025-08-17 12:54:50'),
('b5d6c29b-e916-4959-97c4-05bbb5cd4870', 75, 217, 'https://avatars.mds.yandex.net/get-kinopoisk-image/10900341/999cc6b8-3e77-4041-92c1-d12b7c858c94/1080x', '▫️Short review: Never doubting about James Gunn. He brought us his best work on this new Superman. I absolutely was stunned while watching this. The visual and cinematography are staggering. David Corenswet unmistakably carries the aura of a Superman figure in the way this character is portrayed. ▫️Rating • Plot: 9.0 \n• Twist 8.0 • Message: 9.0 • Acting: 7.8 \n• Cinematography: 9.5 • Pacing: 10 • Visual effect: 9.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 9.0 • Music/OST: 9.0 ▫️Overall: 9.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Superman (2025)', 'DCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/b5d6c29b-e916-4959-97c4-05bbb5cd4870', 4.5, '2025-12-12 10:47:59', '2025-12-12 10:47:59'),
('b5f581c3-9d5c-41f6-9975-0113222db005', 41, 217, 'https://64.media.tumblr.com/6beec56a213578ed3e52ce0d38907cb8/4fc47e83977a8e2a-c6/s1280x1920/4c861db05a32571952aa7720e088713e67ecb5b0.jpg', '▫️Short review: One of the most meticulously crafted and awe-inspiring world-building anime, where a dark, tragic tale as deep as the abyss itself stands in stark contrast to its deceptively cute art style. Made in Abyss will always remain in my top ten favorite anime.', 'Made In Abyss', 'Anime/TV Series | C18', 'Akyl_Lee/b5f581c3-9d5c-41f6-9975-0113222db005', 5.0, '2025-08-27 08:24:10', '2025-08-27 08:24:10'),
('b68b4797-aa77-4143-b7c6-4ca0d1a151a1', 76, 217, 'https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/51b3dc8ee4b051b96ceb10de/1433045109301-LVJQNZE817URG530RHRE/ant-man-movie-fan-art-heroes-dont-get-any-bigger', '▫️Short review: Though not the MCU’s finest, Ant-Man hold a place in top 10 MCU films in my opinion. It presents an unusual hero with a quirky power and a troubled background. This conflict leaves audiences to question what truly defines a hero. ▫️Rating • Plot: 8.8 • Twist: 7.0 • Message: 6.5 • Acting: 7.7 • Cinematography: 8.0 • Pacing: 7.9 • VFX: 9.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 7.0 \n• Music/OST: 8.0▫️Overall: 7.7(⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Ant Man (2015)', 'MCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/b68b4797-aa77-4143-b7c6-4ca0d1a151a1', 3.8, '2025-12-11 09:13:06', '2025-12-11 09:13:06'),
('b75ecb34-532f-485e-8e47-7b014380297a', 56, 217, 'https://lumiere-a.akamaihd.net/v1/images/image002_18870_b56691ea.jpeg?region=0,0,1688,2500', '▫️Short review: Loki embodies Marvel’s artistic ambition on television: a story both philosophical and emotional, transforming a familiar villain beyond the confines of superhero tropes into an epic tragedy that is at once grand and profoundly human.\n ▫️Rating • Plot: 10 • Twist: 9.5\n • Message: 9.0 • Acting: 9.0 \n• Cinematography: 9.4 • Pacing: 8.2 \n• Make up and hairstyling: 8.9 •VFX: 9.5 • Music: 9.0\n▫️Overall: 9.1 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Loki (2021-2023)', 'MCU | 🔝10 TV Series', 'Akyl_Lee/b75ecb34-532f-485e-8e47-7b014380297a', 4.5, '2025-09-05 12:57:33', '2025-09-05 12:57:33'),
('b9a805ff-d9ca-4f4e-b43f-a258a7cf1392', 65, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/819QM8NViPS.jpg', '▫️Short review: Chloé Zhao brought a uniquely singular film, setting it apart entirely from all pre Marvel movies. Its frame unfolds like a work of art—both visually arresting and epic in scope. Its cosmic story with awe and unexpected twists, though the crowded chars leaves minor gaps in the script. Eternals would never be a failure and hardly deserving the hates. ▫️Rating • Plot: 8.5 \n• Twist 8.8 • Acting: 8.8 • Cine: 10 • Pacing: 10 • VFX: 10 • M&HS: 10 • Music: 9.0 ▫️Overall: 9.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Eternals • 2021', 'MCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/b9a805ff-d9ca-4f4e-b43f-a258a7cf1392', 4.5, '2025-11-24 11:47:43', '2025-11-24 11:47:43'),
('b9b80a1e-589c-4a72-bd9c-3d7e90a64a37', 69, 217, 'https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Fk8hEwkWQAIf9M5.jpg', 'Love it!', 'Amime', 'Animeo', 'Akyl_Lee/b9b80a1e-589c-4a72-bd9c-3d7e90a64a37', 4.5, '2025-11-23 12:21:26', '2025-11-23 12:21:26'),
('be9a53c2-07e8-4c24-a724-091bae622404', 47, 217, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/9PSifrJfKl8sy9tBOd5Vcg0jbN6.jpg', '▫️Short review: A remarkable cinematic masterpiece of the 21st century, Parasite embraces the full range of human emotions—joy, humor, tension, anxiety, and an ineffable melancholy. With a masterfully crafted script and a searing commentary on class divisions in Korean society, Bong Joon Ho delivers a film that overwhelms the mind and leaves audiences awestruck, lingering in silent astonishment through its final moments.', 'Parasite (2019)', 'Drama/Dark Comedy', 'Akyl_Lee/be9a53c2-07e8-4c24-a724-091bae622404', 5.0, '2025-08-23 06:41:50', '2025-08-23 06:41:50'),
('bfc5bcd0-cd79-43ca-9b37-21a93bf2c415', 65, 217, 'https://i.ebayimg.com/00/s/MTYwMFgxMDY2/z/jvYAAOSwTLtnkBfI/$_57.JPG?set_id=880000500F', '▫️Short review: A mid debut for the new Captain America, with engaging yet uneven storytelling. Lacking the sharp intensity like The Winter Soldier, and the central conflict feels unresolved. Still, waiting for the new Captain’s return in a future film that recaptures the action-driven spirit of earlier ones. ▫️Rating • Plot: 6.8 • Twist: 6.0 \n• Message: 6.5 • Acting: 7.5 • Cine: 7.0 • Pacing: 7.0 \n• VFX: 7.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 7.0 • Music: 7.5 ▫️Overall: 6.9 (⭐️⭐⭐️)', 'Captain America: Brave New World', 'MCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/bfc5bcd0-cd79-43ca-9b37-21a93bf2c415', 3.4, '2025-11-23 11:22:16', '2025-11-23 11:22:16'),
('bfe0c035-5056-44d9-b5a7-9d50e940a1cc', 34, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNGZiYWRiYjAtODU0NS00YzAzLTk2MzQtZGVlMzVjM2M3MGQ3XkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_.jpg', '▫️Short review: A chilling, nerve-racking experience. With a creative perspective and an inventive script, It Follows instills dread with a slow, creeping inevitability that lingers long after. By the end, your fear of the crowd will have reached an entirely new level.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 9.0 • Twist: 7.8 • Acting: 7.0 \n • Cinematography: 6.5 • Pacing: 7.5\n • VFX: 6.8 • Make up & hairstyling: 8.0 • Music: 8.0\n▫️Overall: 7.5 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'It Follows (2014)', 'B-Horror/Supernatural Horror', 'Akyl_Lee/bfe0c035-5056-44d9-b5a7-9d50e940a1cc', 3.7, '2025-08-28 07:38:41', '2025-08-28 07:38:41'),
('c087eecc-41b6-4b34-aa7a-5ce77e325f3c', 34, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTUxNzYyMjg2N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTExNzExNw@@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_.jpg', '▫️Short review: Bold, inventive, and bitingly satirical, The Cabin in the Woods impresses with a script that defies every horror convention. A pioneering work that breaks free from genre clichés, it delivers shocking twists, a brilliantly constructed world, and a finale that stuns.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 10 • Twist: 9.5 • Acting: 7.0 \n • Cinematography: 7.6 • Pacing: 9.0\n • VFX: 7.7 • Make up and hairstyling: 8.0 \n• Music: 7.5\n▫️Overall: 8.3 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'The Cabin in the Woods (2011)', 'Conspiracy thriller/Monster', 'Akyl_Lee/c087eecc-41b6-4b34-aa7a-5ce77e325f3c', 4.1, '2025-08-28 14:09:37', '2025-08-28 14:09:37'),
('c259220e-496e-48c3-8775-e27c52e76cdd', 76, 217, 'https://mir-s3-cdn-cf.behance.net/project_modules/1400_webp/51aff3146743841.62b595ba09230.jpg', '▫️Short review: As one of the first Asian superheroes to debut in the MCU, Shang-Chi dazzles with kinetic martial arts and a mythic, Eastern-tinged narrative - securing its place among the top 10 Marvel titles not to be missed. ▫️Rating: • Plot: 8.0 • Twist: 7.0 • Message: 8.0 \n• Acting: 7.5 • Cinematography: 8.8 • Pacing: 10 \n• Visual effect: 7.9 • Make up & hairstyling: 8.0 \n• Music/OST: 8.8 ▫️Overall: 8.2 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings', 'MCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/c259220e-496e-48c3-8775-e27c52e76cdd', 4.1, '2025-12-11 09:08:40', '2025-12-11 09:08:40'),
('c3af1e17-a0f8-4054-b485-b272eee2ce9b', 65, 217, 'https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/51b3dc8ee4b051b96ceb10de/1433045109301-LVJQNZE817URG530RHRE/ant-man-movie-fan-art-heroes-dont-get-any-bigger', '▫️Short review: Though not the MCU’s finest, Ant-Man hold a place in top 10 MCU films IMO. It presents an unusual hero with a quirky power and a troubled background. This conflict leaves audiences to question what truly defines a hero. ▫️Rating • Plot: 8.8 • Twist: 7.0 • Message: 6.5 \n• Acting: 7.7 • Cinematography: 8.0 • Pacing: 7.9 \n• VFX: 9.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 7.0\n • Music/OST: 8.0▫️Overall: 7.7(⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Ant Man • 2015', 'MCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/c3af1e17-a0f8-4054-b485-b272eee2ce9b', 3.8, '2025-11-23 11:04:45', '2025-11-23 11:04:45'),
('c565eb14-f35e-4ff6-9b98-b9007fdc6463', 74, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/819QM8NViPS._AC_UF894,1000_QL80_.jpg', '▫️Short review: Chloé Zhao brought a uniquely singular film, setting it apart entirely from all pre Marvel movies. Its frame unfolds like a work of art—both visually arresting and epic in scope. Its cosmic story with awe and unexpected twists, though the crowded chars leaves minor gaps in the script. Eternals would never be a failure and hardly deserving the hates. ▫️Rating • Plot: 8.5\n • Twist 8.8 • Acting: 8.8 • Cine: 10 • Pacing: 10 • VFX: 10 • M&HS: 10 • Music: 9.0 ▫️Overall: 9.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Eternals', 'MCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/c565eb14-f35e-4ff6-9b98-b9007fdc6463', 4.5, '2025-12-08 12:48:23', '2025-12-08 12:48:23'),
('c8a35d75-2b76-49e9-a548-9465118a5297', 16, 71, 'https://api.nga.gov/iiif/99758d9d-c10b-4d02-a198-7e49afb1f3a6/full/!800,800/0/default.jpg', 'Ini bukan cuma lukisan, ini potret dari sebuah momen sederhana yang dibekukan selamanya angin yang berhembus, cahaya yang hangat, dan rasa tenang yang nggak akan pernah Sungguh karya yang indah dari seorang Claude Monet', 'La Promenade', 'Femme à l’ombrelle — Madame Monet et son fils', 'diegormdhn/c8a35d75-2b76-49e9-a548-9465118a5297', 5.0, '2025-08-08 17:37:16', '2025-08-08 17:37:16'),
('c8dd0679-fb94-453c-8379-b43cb888a31c', 48, 217, 'https://bottleneckgallery.com/cdn/shop/products/WandaVision_foil.png?v=1634225556', '▫️Short review: Unexpected and astounding experience. WandaVision is an audacious experiment—merging sitcom nostalgia with superhero spectacle. Beneath its playful form lies a deeply moving exploration of grief and love, anchored by Elizabeth Olsen’s powerful performance.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 10 • Twist: 10 • Message: 9.0 \n• Acting: 10 • Cinematography: 8.8 • Pacing: 8.0 \n• Make up and hairstyling: 8.0 •VFX: 8.9\n• Music: 8.5▫️Overall: 9.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'WandaVision', 'MCU | 🔝10 TV Series', 'Akyl_Lee/c8dd0679-fb94-453c-8379-b43cb888a31c', 4.5, '2025-09-01 13:13:05', '2025-09-01 13:13:05'),
('c9129968-5be0-4abb-86d0-84804941498e', 56, 217, 'https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/51b3dc8ee4b051b96ceb10de/1425567610114-VMD9J9URBP2SSS2KD9NP/iron-man-has-the-upper-hand-in-captain-america-civil-war-fan-poster1', '▫️Short review: Civil War stands as an emblematic confrontation—both a political tragedy and a personal one. The film balances spectacular action with psychological depth, leaving its mark as one of the most pivotal chapters in the MCU.\n ▫️Rating • Plot: 10 • Twist: 8.0 • Message: 8.0 \n• Acting: 8.7 • Cinematography: 8.8 • Pacing: 9.0 \n• VFX: 8.5 • Make up and hairstyling: 8.6\n • Music: 8.0▫️Overall: 8.7 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Captain America: Civil War', 'MCU | 🔝10 Movies', 'Akyl_Lee/c9129968-5be0-4abb-86d0-84804941498e', 4.3, '2025-09-05 09:59:25', '2025-09-05 09:59:25'),
('cb2455cf-51ee-472a-87eb-e3b4ca682d5a', 34, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjNhNTlmYmYtYjcxZi00ZDU1LTkxMWYtYzFlMWMzY2RiODM1XkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_.jpg', '▫️Short review: Constantine (2005) is a dark, stylish dive into the supernatural—mixing noir grit with theological depth. Keanu Reeves anchors the film with cool intensity. Visually striking and thematically rich, it’s an underrated gem that has rightfully earned its cult classic status.', 'Constantine (2005)', 'Supernatural Horror', 'Akyl_Lee/cb2455cf-51ee-472a-87eb-e3b4ca682d5a', 5.0, '2025-09-18 07:46:11', '2025-09-18 07:46:11'),
('ccfb5721-d554-42da-b5e9-ee9138bb9672', 3, 6, 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTojJ0ZyvWchEtMDp3bdNzfzmAUdxS-yUq_6UfN5DIfnXN6Cv-qqMNJPRXd&s=10', 'He can NOT dancing!!!', 'Druski Dancing', 'Druski', 'luker_feller/ccfb5721-d554-42da-b5e9-ee9138bb9672', 4.5, '2025-03-03 00:56:36', '2025-03-03 00:56:36'),
('ce0f7244-40ac-4728-9eb8-b52fd5e54e89', 74, 217, 'https://avatars.mds.yandex.net/get-kinopoisk-image/1773646/a99692a7-d063-4566-b76a-da3d9fa4c34b/1080x', '▫️Short review: Genuinely and perfectly stunning in every frame. Great storyline and breathtaking world-building. Never been into magic stuff but after watching this, my mind changed due to its awesomeness. Dr.Strange also has a deep and meaningful message on the philosophy of life. ▫️Rating • Plot: 10 • Twist 9.0 • Acting: 8.5 \n• Cinematography: 10 • Pacing: 9.0 • Visual effect: 10 • Make up and hairstyling: 10 • Music/OST: 9.0 ▫️Overall: 9.3 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Doctor Strange (2016)', 'MCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/ce0f7244-40ac-4728-9eb8-b52fd5e54e89', 4.8, '2025-12-08 12:18:01', '2025-12-08 12:18:01'),
('ce241c04-f996-413b-8758-bd0406c46c5e', 34, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzc3OWFhZWItMTE2Yy00N2NmLTg1YTktNGVlNDY0ODQ5YjNlXkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_.jpg', '▫️Short review: What a comeback! Don’t even expect this sequel to be this good. Bringing the “Bloodlines” detail is the genius idea. Well-crafted character conflicts. Having creative POV and unpredictable twist. This stands as the strongest one of the franchise, serving almost as the final piece of a large picture.\n▫️Rating: • Plot: 8.0 • Twist: 8.0 • Acting: 6.5 • Cinematography: 6.8 • Pacing: 10 • Visual effect: 7.5 • Make up & hairstyling: 9.0 • Music/OST: 6.5\n▫️Overall: 7.8 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Final Destination: Bloodlines (2025) | R', 'Splatter/Supernatural Horror', 'Akyl_Lee/ce241c04-f996-413b-8758-bd0406c46c5e', 3.9, '2025-08-18 23:00:33', '2025-08-18 23:00:33');
INSERT INTO `vibe_others` (`id`, `category_other_id`, `user_id`, `image_url`, `comment`, `title`, `desc`, `path`, `rating`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
('d0798caf-8a8a-4bb4-a262-93a34d9fc1db', 56, 217, 'https://cdn.noron.vn/2018/12/03/f6454eba0de72402fc9186da9883c496.jpg', '▫️Short review: By centering Thanos as a tragic yet terrifying figure, the film delivers both grandeur and emotional weight. With impeccable pacing, groundbreaking visual effects, and an audacious ending that stunned global audiences, it stands as one of Marvel’s most daring and impactful achievements. ▫️Rating • Plot: 10 • Twist: 10 • Acting: 9.5 • Message: 8.0 • Cine: 9.0 • Pacing: 10 • VFX: 8.0 • MU&H: 8.9 • Music: 9.6 ▫️Overall: 9.2 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Avengers: Infinity War', 'MCU | 🔝10 Movies', 'Akyl_Lee/d0798caf-8a8a-4bb4-a262-93a34d9fc1db', 4.6, '2025-09-05 06:57:15', '2025-09-05 06:57:15'),
('d4db5b6a-07f0-453a-9f74-b41f766b339e', 56, 217, 'https://mir-s3-cdn-cf.behance.net/project_modules/max_1200/a8ff05169962173.64556e12a369f.jpg', '▫️Short review: Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3 delivers an emotionally charged finale, blending vibrant spectacle with heartfelt storytelling. Anchored by Rocket’s poignant arc, it balances humor, action, and genuine pathos, marking one of the MCU’s most resonant entries.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 9.5 • Twist: 8.0 • Message: 10\n• Acting: 8.8 • Cinematography: 8.9 • Pacing: 10\n• Make up & Hairstyling: 10 •VFX: 9.0\n• Music: 8.5▫️Overall: 9.1 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/d4db5b6a-07f0-453a-9f74-b41f766b339e', 4.5, '2025-09-05 11:33:48', '2025-09-05 11:33:48'),
('d4f805f5-decc-47a8-9f31-83f871000baf', 54, 217, 'https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/f/fdeafbe9-a5bf-4f58-92da-beb3496b5dfe/d8qf4kw-cfa13b8a-df8e-445e-aa83-66716d6decf7.jpg/v1/fill/w_734,h_1088,q_70,strp/the_winter_soldier__poster_textless__by_darkhawk41_d8qf4kw-pre.jpg?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..z3r13LfrXjwTY9-iHjmy0hlRvoqlL_S12oYtxjTh8GU', '▫️Short review: A superhero film of absolute perfection, Captain America: The Winter Soldier balances politics and action with precision. Its spectacular, gripping fight sequences and tightly crafted, layered script have made it the benchmark for MCU films in the years that followed.', 'Captain America: The Winter Soldier', 'MCU | 🔝10 Movies', 'Akyl_Lee/d4f805f5-decc-47a8-9f31-83f871000baf', 5.0, '2025-09-05 03:51:20', '2025-09-05 03:51:20'),
('d501166e-7ef2-4ce8-9e69-85eced45c442', 67, 217, 'https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/f/bb48ffc1-bf25-486b-a056-63c3bfce1223/df3fedk-4d1556e1-cfc1-41b0-9e19-f6dc54324e1c.jpg?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..KpxV3a1MPhzCFFGJnyJfNaBVwC1HW2akEIwmpS8g9HY', '▫️Short review: Beyond expectations, the new season of Peacemaker unveils a previously unexplored dimension of Christopher Smith’s emotional and psychological depths. This installment delivers a dynamic range of tones—at once surprising, darkly humorous, and quietly resonant. \n▫️Rating: \n• Plot: 8.8 \n• Twist: 9.0 \n• Message: 9.0 • Acting: 9.5 \n• Cinematography: 9.8 \n• Pacing: 10 \n• VFX: 8.9 \n• Make up & hairstyling: 9.6 \n• Music: 8.0 \n▫️Overall: 9.1 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Peacemaker • SS2 [2025]', 'DCU | 🔝 10 Series', 'Akyl_Lee/d501166e-7ef2-4ce8-9e69-85eced45c442', 4.5, '2025-11-23 11:46:38', '2025-11-23 11:46:38'),
('d71e9b7c-68db-4d3f-9995-8191b64ba4e7', 56, 217, 'https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/f/7a17c932-dd94-484c-9e11-3891edee15d4/dg40ri8-ebc6da6f-67d4-425e-98c5-bcebba4f66f3.jpg?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..MJn6T44UUGbFwTfzKt_p-7wNLUDKNUpi-mBRo9cSAi0', '▫️Short review: In fact, I had higher expectations for this installment. Certain flaws in the script disrupted both the emotional rhythm and the viewing experience. Nevertheless, the film delivers impressively on fan service, offering spectacular battle sequences and the return of familiar characters in this third chapter.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 7.0 • Twist: 9.0 • Message: 8.4 • Acting: 9.0 \n• Cinematography: 8.0 • Pacing: 7.0 • VFX: 8.0 \n• MU&H: 8.0 • Music: 7.0▫️Overall: 7.9 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Spider-Man: No Way Home', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/d71e9b7c-68db-4d3f-9995-8191b64ba4e7', 3.9, '2025-09-05 09:50:15', '2025-09-05 09:50:15'),
('d8245a6b-f339-4dc1-bb2c-8313d2145dcf', 32, 217, 'https://cdn.marvel.com/content/1x/thunderboltsposter.jpeg', '▫️Short review: Absolutely cinema! The best Marvel movie after Avengers: End Game. Love the way Marvel introduced its new character. The message hit me hard. The movie itself is not about saving the world, it’s about saving oneself. The ending might catch you off guard!!!\n\n▫️Rating • Plot: 7.0 • Twist: 7.0 • Message: 9.0 • Acting: 8.0 • Cinematography: 9.0 • Pacing: 7.0 • Visual effect: 8.5 • Make up and hairstyling: 8.0 • Music / OST: 7.0 ▫️Overal: 7.8 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Thunderbolts*', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/d8245a6b-f339-4dc1-bb2c-8313d2145dcf', 3.9, '2025-08-17 13:14:01', '2025-08-17 13:14:01'),
('d8a754db-17a3-4880-aeaa-f4d56571ca65', 34, 217, 'https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/521dec4de4b0912f523f3b56/1696087974266-3S8UKZX03Y04KC83JIDP/no-one-will-save-you-poster.jpg?format=2500w', '▫️Short review: Beyond expectation with familiar alien theme but striking effectiveness. Tense pacing and various unforeseen turns . The female lead’s well-built. She delivers deeply satisfying moments of action. This film deserves more discussion.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 8.5 • Twist: 7.8 • Message: 6.0 • Acting: 7.8 • Cinematography: 8.0 • Pacing: 9.0 • Visual effect: 8.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 8.0 • Music/OST: 7.5\n▫️Overall: 7.8 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'No one will save you (2023)', 'Horror Sci-Fi/ Mystery', 'Akyl_Lee/d8a754db-17a3-4880-aeaa-f4d56571ca65', 3.9, '2025-08-24 10:18:34', '2025-08-24 10:18:34'),
('da6ab308-2dc5-4620-be01-bc2e8f4b0837', 72, 217, 'https://avatars.mds.yandex.net/get-kinopoisk-image/4716873/f64d822e-3c63-48a4-bed4-dbabdedb222d/1080x', '▫️Short review: Meditative,  elegiac & unique. Arrival reimagines science fiction as a philosophical inquiry into language, memory, and human connection. Denis Villeneuve’s restrained direction and Amy Adams’s quietly powerful performance anchor the film’s exploration of time and grief, creating a work that is both intellectually compelling and emotionally resonant.', 'Arrival (2016)', 'Sci-Fi/Drama', 'Akyl_Lee/da6ab308-2dc5-4620-be01-bc2e8f4b0837', 5.0, '2025-12-06 10:35:27', '2025-12-06 10:35:27'),
('dae8dba5-4e8e-422b-9424-5db712fca28e', 72, 217, 'https://avatars.mds.yandex.net/get-kinopoisk-image/1599028/1cd75f40-9d64-4680-8543-8dbe11b6abd2/1080x', '▫️Short review: Breathtaking, striking, and visually explosive, with a narrative that transcends the imagination of its era— Inception rightfully stands as one of Christopher Nolan’s towering masterpieces of the past two decades.', 'Inception (2010)', 'Sci-Fi/Action Epic', 'Akyl_Lee/dae8dba5-4e8e-422b-9424-5db712fca28e', 5.0, '2025-12-06 11:02:34', '2025-12-06 11:02:34'),
('db12b0a0-4405-48d7-8fc8-6b49f36c32fb', 46, 217, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/9PSifrJfKl8sy9tBOd5Vcg0jbN6.jpg', 'A remarkable cinematic masterpiece of the 21st century, Parasite embraces the full range of human emotions—joy, humor, tension, anxiety, and an ineffable melancholy. With a masterfully crafted script and a searing commentary on class divisions in Korean society, Bong Joon Ho delivers a film that overwhelms the mind and leaves audiences awestruck, lingering in silent astonishment through its final moments.', 'Parasite (2019)', 'Drama/Dark Comedy', 'Akyl_Lee/db12b0a0-4405-48d7-8fc8-6b49f36c32fb', 5.0, '2025-08-23 05:56:50', '2025-08-23 05:56:50'),
('db386f0c-e1b0-49fa-8991-65a305fdf07f', 41, 217, 'https://pbs.twimg.com/media/GjmxW0faIAEWevq?format=jpg&name=4096x4096', '▫️Short review: Overwhelming and immersive, Ne Zha enchants with visuals akin to surreal wonders, elevating the viewing experience to the whole new level. Its story is engaging, humorous, and concise, punctuated by twists that are surprised and unpredictable.', 'Ne Zha 2: Mo tong nao hai (2025)', 'Animation | T13', 'Akyl_Lee/db386f0c-e1b0-49fa-8991-65a305fdf07f', 5.0, '2025-08-24 10:55:32', '2025-08-24 10:55:32'),
('db567dae-10af-4a72-b7f0-a8d4acccd093', 52, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BY2I2NzJmY2YtYTM3Ni00ZGJhLThkZTItODFhMzhlZjZkMDQ5XkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_.jpg', '▫️Short review: A story ripe with potential yet unevenly realized. The first act builds a tense, chilling atmosphere with promise, but from the second act onward the narrative slips into predictability and waning intrigue. The finale, while serviceable, lacks the dramatic force to deliver a truly impactful climax.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 7.0 • Twist: 5.0 • Acting: 8.0 \n • Cinematography: 8.0 • Pacing: 7.0\n • VFX: 7.5 • Make up & hairstyling: 8.0 • Music: 7.0\n▫️Overall: 7.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Talk To Me (2022)', 'Supernatural/Body Horror', 'Akyl_Lee/db567dae-10af-4a72-b7f0-a8d4acccd093', 3.5, '2025-08-28 09:50:57', '2025-08-28 09:50:57'),
('db6be5c3-3b3b-46ad-b03c-7ca5ee7bc55a', 56, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/911flUKGxzL.jpg', '▫️Short review: Humorous, eye-catching, and unexpectedly moving, GOTG Vol. 2 evokes a wide range of emotions by bringing MCU fans a distinctive experience, transporting them into a boundless universe while weaving its cosmic storytelling with wit and intelligence. The chemistry among its characters remains undeniable. \n▫️Rating • Plot: 8.8 • Twist: 8.5\n • Message: 6.0 • Acting: 8.0 • Cine: 9.0\n • Pacing: 8.5 • VFX: 9.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 9.0 \n• Music: 8.8 ▫️Overall: 8.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2', 'MCU | 🔝10 Movies', 'Akyl_Lee/db6be5c3-3b3b-46ad-b03c-7ca5ee7bc55a', 4.0, '2025-09-05 11:54:34', '2025-09-05 11:54:34'),
('dda6131c-47f7-4044-a760-f0082b795897', 56, 217, 'https://mir-s3-cdn-cf.behance.net/project_modules/max_1200_webp/14268d217212319.678d34825bd81.jpg', '▫️Short review: A mid debut for the new Captain America, with engaging yet uneven storytelling. Lacking the sharp intensity like The Winter Soldier, and the central conflict feels unresolved. Still, waiting for the new Captain’s return in a future film that recaptures the action-driven spirit of earlier ones. ▫️Rating • Plot: 6.8 • Twist: 6.0 \n• Message: 6.5 • Acting: 7.5 • Cinematography: 7.0 • Pacing: 7.0 • VFX: 7.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 7.0 • Music / OST: 7.5 ▫️Overall: 6.9 (⭐️⭐⭐️)', 'Captain America: Brave New World', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/dda6131c-47f7-4044-a760-f0082b795897', 3.4, '2025-09-05 07:52:56', '2025-09-05 07:52:56'),
('ddee2dc7-9b6c-41a4-a139-ba7e32cd2e2f', 64, 217, 'https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/51b3dc8ee4b051b96ceb10de/1433045109301-LVJQNZE817URG530RHRE/ant-man-movie-fan-art-heroes-dont-get-any-bigger', '▫️Short review: Though not the MCU’s finest, Ant-Man hold a place in top 10 MCU films IMO. It presents an unusual hero with a quirky power and a troubled background. This conflict leaves audiences to question what truly defines a hero. ▫️Rating • Plot: 8.8 • Twist: 7.0 • Message: 6.5\n • Acting: 7.7 • Cinematography: 8.0 • Pacing: 7.9 \n• VFX: 9.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 7.0 \n• Music/OST: 8.0\n▫️Overall: 7.7(⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Ant Man • 2015', 'MCU | 🔝 10 MCU films', 'Akyl_Lee/ddee2dc7-9b6c-41a4-a139-ba7e32cd2e2f', 3.8, '2025-11-21 07:32:24', '2025-11-21 07:32:24'),
('de418d53-e65c-43b5-a2ae-1730ef62ef31', 72, 217, 'https://cdn.displate.com/artwork/857x1200/2024-12-19/631ca90e-c9d9-4ee2-8f9e-48bc2c006f81.jpg', '▫️Short review: Profound, visually arresting, and emotionally resonant, “Interstellar” (2014) stands as a remarkable synthesis of scientific ambition and human sentiment. Nolan’s precise direction and Hoyte van Hoytema’s sweeping cinematography shape a narrative that interrogates time, survival, and love with academic rigor. Anchored by McConaughey’s compelling performance, the film remains a sophisticated meditation on humanity’s pursuit of purpose among the stars.', 'Interstellar (2014)', 'Sci-Fi', 'Akyl_Lee/de418d53-e65c-43b5-a2ae-1730ef62ef31', 5.0, '2025-12-06 11:18:03', '2025-12-06 11:18:03'),
('e160c498-adf2-4069-8c18-a98feeb8d5af', 53, 217, 'https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/f/fdeafbe9-a5bf-4f58-92da-beb3496b5dfe/d8qf4kw-cfa13b8a-df8e-445e-aa83-66716d6decf7.jpg/v1/fill/w_734,h_1088,q_70,strp/the_winter_soldier__poster_textless__by_darkhawk41_d8qf4kw-pre.jpg?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..z3r13LfrXjwTY9-iHjmy0hlRvoqlL_S12oYtxjTh8GU', '▫️Short review: A superhero film of absolute perfection, Captain America: The Winter Soldier balances politics and action with precision. Its spectacular, gripping fight sequences and tightly crafted, layered script have made it the benchmark for MCU films in the years that followed.', 'Captain America: The Winter Soldier', 'MCU | 🔝10 Movies', 'Akyl_Lee/e160c498-adf2-4069-8c18-a98feeb8d5af', 5.0, '2025-09-05 03:44:03', '2025-09-05 03:44:03'),
('e1f5b226-bf2f-482a-a6e1-d81be0f80911', 65, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81W8yPIxOlL.jpg', 'Stands out for deft balance of humor, action, and emotional nuance. Expanding the MCU’s cosmic scope while crafting a compelling ensemble whose personal wounds and motivations deepen the narrative. Its tight pacing, striking visual design, and nostalgic soundtrack elevate the story beyond superhero fare, underscoring themes of connection, identity, and chosen family.\n▫️Rating: • Plot: 8.8 • Twist: 7.8 • Acting: 9.0 • Cine: 9.5 • Pacing: 8.0 • VFX: 9.0 • MU&H: 9.8 • Music: 9.0\n▫️Overall: 8.8 ⭐️⭐⭐', 'Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 1', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/e1f5b226-bf2f-482a-a6e1-d81be0f80911', 4.4, '2025-11-25 13:38:08', '2025-11-25 13:38:08'),
('e5202060-a9c1-4e2a-b2d1-29c5d4bbb974', 34, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTQzNzg0NDI2MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzgxNzY2MTE@._V1_.jpg', '▫️Short review: As a big fan of the found footage genre, I was genuinely satisfied with this film. Its gripping story, unexpected turns, and claustrophobic setting create constant tension—an underrated work that, for me, was an outstanding horror experience.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 7.8 • Twist: 9.0 • Acting: 7.0\n • Cine: 6.8 • Pacing: 7.5 • VFX: 7.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 7.5 • Music: 7.8\n▫️Overall: 7.5 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'As Above So Below (2014)', 'Found Footage Horror', 'Akyl_Lee/e5202060-a9c1-4e2a-b2d1-29c5d4bbb974', 3.7, '2025-08-27 08:55:45', '2025-08-27 08:55:45'),
('e642bcbc-1cd0-4d74-a2db-fc61abcccadc', 47, 217, 'https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ewpf_EEUYAEMZY5.jpg', '▫️Short review: Profound, visually arresting, and emotionally resonant, “Interstellar” (2014) stands as a remarkable synthesis of scientific ambition and human sentiment. Nolan’s precise direction and Hoyte van Hoytema’s sweeping cinematography shape a narrative that interrogates time, survival, and love with academic rigor. Anchored by McConaughey’s compelling performance, the film remains a sophisticated meditation on humanity’s pursuit of purpose among the stars.', 'Interstellar • 2014', 'Sci-Fi', 'Akyl_Lee/e642bcbc-1cd0-4d74-a2db-fc61abcccadc', 5.0, '2025-11-26 07:15:38', '2025-11-26 07:15:38'),
('e7976dce-da0b-494e-bd17-e85098c1d0d3', 65, 217, 'https://mir-s3-cdn-cf.behance.net/project_modules/fs/a8b0fd132117385.61a2ad5d83d0f.png', '▫️Short review: In fact, I had higher expectations for this installment. Certain flaws in the script disrupted both the emotional rhythm and the viewing experience. Nevertheless, the film delivers impressively on fan service, offering spectacular battle sequences and the return of familiar characters in this third chapter. ▫️Rating • Plot: 7.0 • Twist: 9.0 • Message: 8.4 • Acting: 9.0 \n• Cinematography: 8.0 • Pacing: 7.0 • VFX: 8.0 \n• MU&H: 8.0 • Music: 7.0▫️Overall: 7.9 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Spider-Man: No Way Home', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/e7976dce-da0b-494e-bd17-e85098c1d0d3', 3.9, '2025-11-25 12:45:02', '2025-11-25 12:45:02'),
('ead8b984-b400-49d7-b494-da82aa12a79f', 44, 217, 'https://cdn.tgdd.vn//GameApp/-1//review-phim-inception-ke-danh-cap-giac-mo-2-800x450.jpg', 'Overwhelming, striking, and visually explosive, with a narrative that transcends the imagination of its era—Inception rightfully stands as one of Christopher Nolan’s most monumental achievements of the past two decades.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 10 • Twist: 10 • Message: 10 • Acting: 10 • Cinematography: 10 • Pacing: 10 • Visual effect: 10 • Make up and hairstyling: 10 • Music / OST: 10▫️Overal: 10 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Inception (2010)', 'Sci-Fi', 'Akyl_Lee/ead8b984-b400-49d7-b494-da82aa12a79f', 5.0, '2025-08-22 08:56:44', '2025-08-22 08:56:44'),
('ec9318a1-a27e-4e81-bcb8-d557c9e83cba', 72, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjJhNTYxOGUtYWQxMS00YjYwLWFmMWItOWViN2QyZmZhNDM3XkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_.jpg', '▫️Short review: Genuinely unique- a thrilling and unparalleled experience. Under Baz Poonpiriya’s direction, the schoolyard theme comes to life with unprecedented vibrancy and allure. A tightly crafted script, charged with suspense, surprising twists, and profound message.', 'Bad Genius (2017)', 'Crime/Drama', 'Akyl_Lee/ec9318a1-a27e-4e81-bcb8-d557c9e83cba', 5.0, '2025-12-06 10:46:19', '2025-12-06 10:46:19'),
('ed840659-a2d5-4050-a673-8dee65723d99', 74, 217, 'https://avatars.mds.yandex.net/get-kinopoisk-image/6201401/c837fe6f-0c5b-459e-8b6d-2c10b56718b2/1080x', '▫️Short review: Moon Knight is a distinctive superhero work, blending psychological complexity with mythological intrigue, elevated by Oscar Isaac’s remarkable performance. Though its narrative lacks full cohesion, the series stands as a bold and singular experiment within the MCU. ▫️Rating • Plot: 9.5 • Twist: 9.0 \n• Message: 8.0 • Acting: 10 • Cinematography: 8.8 \n• Pacing: 7.8 • Make up and hairstyling: 10 • Music: 9.5 ▫️Overall: 9.0 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Moon Knight (2022)', 'MCU • TV Series | 🔝10 Series', 'Akyl_Lee/ed840659-a2d5-4050-a673-8dee65723d99', 4.5, '2025-12-08 12:37:25', '2025-12-08 12:37:25'),
('ef680941-d704-4a73-bfae-c0db327d6fb8', 34, 217, 'https://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/394AAOSwcmVf7DiV/s-l1200.jpg', '▫️Short review: Haunting, dark, and eerie—James Wan has always had a knack for crafting twists that leave audiences stunned. Following Saw, Dead Silence may be regarded as a step back in his career, yet it remains a solid horror entry that will satisfy fans of the genre.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 7.5 • Twist: 10 • Acting: 6.5\n• Cinematography: 7.8 • Pacing: 8.0 • VFX: 7.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 8.0 • Music: 8.0▫️Overall: 7.8(⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Dead Silence (2007)', 'Supernatural Horror', 'Akyl_Lee/ef680941-d704-4a73-bfae-c0db327d6fb8', 3.9, '2025-08-31 13:49:25', '2025-08-31 13:49:25'),
('f3b1bd04-0c19-43fa-8ea7-05eeb2a1b3a1', 65, 217, 'https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/51b3dc8ee4b051b96ceb10de/1725469197767-HDTVFHZ476OAQ71FHJ7Y/Screenshot+2024-09-04+at+9.57.09%E2%80%AFAM.jpg', '▫️Short review: A spellbinding world of magic—haunting, alluring, and full of surprises. Agatha All Along shatters all prior doubts with a screenplay that is both masterful and layered. Viewers are drawn as if under enchantment, only to be jolted by the film’s startling turns. ▫️Rating • Plot: 10 • Twist: 10 • Message: 8.5 • Acting: 9.5 • Cinematography: 8.8 • Pacing: 8.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 10 • Music: 10▫️Overall: 9.1 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Agatha All Along • 2024', 'MCU • TV Series | 🔝 10 Series', 'Akyl_Lee/f3b1bd04-0c19-43fa-8ea7-05eeb2a1b3a1', 4.5, '2025-11-24 12:03:18', '2025-11-24 12:03:18'),
('f5246d06-a4b9-4406-b6f3-c893f59443cb', 34, 217, 'https://mir-s3-cdn-cf.behance.net/project_modules/hd/38f99667280563.5b33eb0290810.png', '▫️Short review: Get Out (2017) is a landmark in contemporary horror, blending social critique with psychological suspense. Jordan Peele crafts a narrative that is both entertaining and deeply unsettling, exposing racial anxieties through the lens of genre filmmaking. With sharp twists, strong performances, and a resonant message, the film redefines horror as a vehicle for cultural commentary.', 'Get Out (2017)', 'Thriller/Suspense Mystery', 'Akyl_Lee/f5246d06-a4b9-4406-b6f3-c893f59443cb', 5.0, '2025-09-06 08:22:46', '2025-09-06 08:22:46'),
('f6852253-e3d4-4a6d-ba60-a2cd824fcba1', 71, 6, 'https://images.genius.com/2da322648704159878b73c5cfc9c7dc5.1000x1000x1.png', 'Conspiracy theorist screaming Illuminati\nThey can\'t believe this much skill is in the human body', 'Heaven', 'JAY-Z', 'luker_feller/f6852253-e3d4-4a6d-ba60-a2cd824fcba1', 4.0, '2025-11-25 17:43:15', '2025-11-25 17:43:15'),
('f78bef4d-2246-44b3-b7b6-4e65a72dc04d', 65, 217, 'https://avatars.mds.yandex.net/get-kinopoisk-image/4483445/ef0bbcd1-22c9-477f-a33a-e3d385d5b046/1080x', '▫️Short review: Absolute cinema! Love the way Marvel introduced its new character. The message hit me hard. The movie itself is not about saving the world, it’s about saving oneself. The ending might catch you off guard!!! ▫️Rating • Plot: 7.0 • Twist: 7.0 • Message: 9.0 • Acting: 8.0\n • Cinematography: 9.0 • Pacing: 7.0 • Visual effect: 8.5 • Make up and hairstyling: 8.0\n • Music / OST: 7.0 ▫️Overall: 7.8 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Thunderbolts*', 'MCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/f78bef4d-2246-44b3-b7b6-4e65a72dc04d', 3.9, '2025-12-07 07:30:06', '2025-12-07 07:30:06'),
('f964c117-e8e0-4528-a7fe-984185916eb0', 76, 217, 'https://i.ebayimg.com/00/s/MTYwMFgxMDY2/z/jvYAAOSwTLtnkBfI/$_57.JPG?set_id=880000500F', '▫️Short review: A mid debut for the new Captain America, with engaging yet uneven storytelling. Lacking the sharp intensity like The Winter Soldier, and the central conflict feels unresolved. Still, waiting for the new Captain’s return in a future film that recaptures the action-driven spirit of earlier ones. ▫️Rating • Plot: 6.8 • Twist: 6.0 \n• Message: 6.5 • Acting: 7.5 • Cinematography: 7.0 \n• Pacing: 7.0 • VFX: 7.0 \n• Make up and hairstyling: 7.0 • Music / OST: 7.5 ▫️Overall: 6.9 (⭐️⭐⭐️)', 'Captain America: Brave New World', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/f964c117-e8e0-4528-a7fe-984185916eb0', 3.4, '2025-12-11 22:32:27', '2025-12-11 22:32:27'),
('f9671a32-3827-4bc0-832a-504e0585b2b7', 48, 217, 'https://kenh14cdn.com/203336854389633024/2021/9/6/photo-1-1630910157623154379141.jpeg', '▫️Short review: As one of the first Asian superheroes to debut in the MCU, Shang-Chi dazzles with kinetic martial arts and a mythic, Eastern-tinged narrative - securing its place among the top 10 Marvel titles not to be missed.\n▫️Rating: • Plot: 8.0 • Twist: 7.0 • Message: 8.0  \n• Acting: 7.5 • Cinematography: 8.8 • Pacing: 10 • Visual effect: 7.9 • Make up & hairstyling: 8.0 • Music/OST: 8.8\n▫️Overall: 8.2 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings', 'MCU | 🔝10', 'Akyl_Lee/f9671a32-3827-4bc0-832a-504e0585b2b7', 4.1, '2025-08-23 09:03:54', '2025-08-23 09:03:54'),
('f9727df4-2634-4eba-9da4-31053b5d7000', 52, 217, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81iRFJ++hBS._UF894,1000_QL80_.jpg', '▫️Short review: Haunting, harrowing, dark, and singularly disturbing—Hereditary terrifies without resorting to cheap jump scares. Its unconventional storytelling and unrelenting tension culminate in scenes of unbearable intensity. Anchored by the electrifying performances, especially Toni Collette’s tour de force—an Oscar-worthy portrayal of unhinged brilliance.', 'Hereditary (2018)', 'Supernatural Horror', 'Akyl_Lee/f9727df4-2634-4eba-9da4-31053b5d7000', 5.0, '2025-08-27 09:40:11', '2025-08-27 09:40:11'),
('f9bc3bde-52a6-4191-897c-72b5b49cce87', 77, 217, 'https://cdn.marvel.com/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/a0/5903bfb656850/clean.jpg', 'Good', 'Vol3', 'Mcu', 'Akyl_Lee/f9bc3bde-52a6-4191-897c-72b5b49cce87', 4.0, '2025-12-11 09:49:09', '2025-12-11 09:49:09'),
('facce0f1-c937-4209-97eb-eab425d21490', 71, 6, 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRJduGTjin3B2Tzj9uHQV-RJ07JD7P68z-HWw&usqp=CAU', 'The world is yours, but the city’s mine', 'Pipe Down', 'Drake', 'luker_feller/facce0f1-c937-4209-97eb-eab425d21490', 4.3, '2025-11-25 17:37:09', '2025-11-25 17:37:09'),
('fe0cc3d5-9a8b-4aa0-b895-ef930caf86c1', 76, 217, 'https://mir-s3-cdn-cf.behance.net/project_modules/max_1200_webp/a8b0fd132117385.61a2ad5d83d0f.png', '▫️Short review: In fact, I had higher expectations for this installment. Certain flaws in the script disrupted both the emotional rhythm and the viewing experience. Nevertheless, the film delivers impressively on fan service, offering spectacular battle sequences and the return of familiar characters in this third chapter. ▫️Rating • Plot: 7.0 • Twist: 9.0 • Message: 8.4 • Acting: 9.0 \n• Cinematography: 8.0 • Pacing: 7.0 • VFX: 8.0 \n• MU&H: 8.0 • Music: 7.0▫️Overall: 7.9 (⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Spider-Man: No Way Home', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/fe0cc3d5-9a8b-4aa0-b895-ef930caf86c1', 3.9, '2025-12-11 09:37:43', '2025-12-11 09:37:43'),
('fe6b06ac-c231-47c6-81cf-694784693efe', 76, 217, 'https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/51b3dc8ee4b051b96ceb10de/1425567610114-VMD9J9URBP2SSS2KD9NP/iron-man-has-the-upper-hand-in-captain-america-civil-war-fan-poster1', '▫️Short review: Civil War stands as an emblematic confrontation—both a political tragedy and a personal one. The film balances spectacular action with psychological depth, leaving its mark as one of the most pivotal chapters in the MCU. ▫️Rating • Plot: 10 • Twist: 8.0 • Message: 8.0 • Acting: 8.7 • Cinematography: 8.8 • Pacing: 9.0 • VFX: 8.5 • Make up and hairstyling: 8.6 • Music: 8.0▫️Overall: 8.7 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Captain America: Civil War', 'MCU', 'Akyl_Lee/fe6b06ac-c231-47c6-81cf-694784693efe', 4.3, '2025-12-11 22:26:23', '2025-12-11 22:26:23'),
('ffc9e262-ccec-47f6-a723-175a32e87b56', 76, 217, 'https://mir-s3-cdn-cf.behance.net/project_modules/1400_webp/a8ff05169962173.64556e12a369f.jpg', '▫️Short review: Poignant, visceral, redemptive. GOTG3 delivers a sharply focused and emotionally charged conclusion to James Gunn’s trilogy. The film confronts the disturbing realities of animal abuse through Rocket’s backstory, using it not for spectacle but as a thematic axis that interrogates ethics of creation. \n▫️Rating • Plot: 8.5 • Twist: 6.8 • Acting: 9.0 • Message: 10 • Cine: 8.8 • Pacing: 9.0 • VFX: 8.5 • MU&H: 8.5 • Music: 8.0 ▫️Overall: 8.5 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'Guardians of the Galaxy Vol.3', 'MCU | 🔝 10 Films', 'Akyl_Lee/ffc9e262-ccec-47f6-a723-175a32e87b56', 4.2, '2025-12-11 09:22:56', '2025-12-11 09:22:56'),
('fff87dd1-7c12-48a8-afe4-bf0629edfb62', 34, 217, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/3dT9xu8pGeHFlOxScWQP8KPGYw8.jpg', '▫️Short review: An experience of suffocating intensity and relentless terror from the very first frame to the last. The Descent transforms the fear of enclosed spaces into an unprecedented cinematic nightmare.\n▫️Rating • Plot: 8:6 • Twist: 8.0 • Acting: 7.8 \n• Cinematography: 7.0 • Pacing: 9.0 • VFX: 8.0 • Make up and hairstyling: 9.5 • Music: 9.0▫️Overall: 8.3 (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️)', 'The Descent (2005)', 'Folk Horror', 'Akyl_Lee/fff87dd1-7c12-48a8-afe4-bf0629edfb62', 4.2, '2025-08-31 13:17:23', '2025-08-31 13:17:23');
